sample-rds-db2-tools.code-workspace
.DS_Store

# Terraform artifacts (apply to all tools/*/Terraform projects)
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.backup
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*

# Real terraform.tfvars (keep .example templates)
**/terraform.tfvars
!**/terraform.tfvars.example

# Terraform crash and override files
crash.log
crash.*.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

